# Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---------|------------|
| Base OS | Ubuntu LTS |
| Backend | Python |
| System Services | Rust |
| Frontend | React + Tauri |
| AI Runtime | Ollama |
| Databases | PostgreSQL, Neo4j, Qdrant |
| Messaging | NATS |
| API | FastAPI |
| Containers | Docker |
| Vision | YOLO, SAM, PaddleOCR |
| Speech | Whisper.cpp, Piper, OpenWakeWord |
| Automation | Playwright, PyAutoGUI |
| Version Control | Git + GitHub |

