# Future Vision

Jarvis OS is not intended to be another chatbot or desktop assistant.

It aims to become a complete AI-native operating system where reasoning, memory, perception, planning, and automation are built into the core computing experience.

The project is being developed as a fully open-source initiative with the goal of creating a platform that anyone can use, contribute to, and build upon.
